<nav class="mcp-pagination" aria-label="Page navigation">
    {{{renderPagination pagination baseUrl=baseUrl pageParamName="page" maxPagesToShow=5}}}
</nav>

{{!--
    This partial assumes:
    - A Handlebars helper `renderPagination` is registered and generates the <ul>...</ul> HTML.
      The helper itself should handle the case where totalPages <= 1 by returning an empty string or minimal markup.
    - The context passed to this partial includes:
        - `pagination`: An object with at least `currentPage`, `totalPages`, `limit`.
        - `baseUrl`: A string representing the base URL for pagination links, including all
                     relevant query parameters except for 'page'.
--}}
